data.description: OPEN HOUSE HAS BEEN CANCELED!!!MOTIVATED SELLER. OFFERING 5K IN CLOSING COSTS. Beautifully maintained home in Mustang Place Subdivision with open concept living and split bedrooms giving the primary bedroom privacy. NO HOA, NO MUD OR PID Taxes. Other features include an office with custom built ins including desk and shelving, kitchen island Quartz countertop. Large master with sitting area, ensuite bath, separate tub and shower, dual sinks, walk-in closet with direct access to the utility room. Living room spacious enough for a very large sectional. Owner added a 12X30 covered porch with ceiling fans to enjoy the outdoors in comfort. (Owner has permit from city). Outside also features landscaping, sprinkler system, French drain and lovely rock pathway near gate. Room for freezer, toolbox & work bench in garage. Conveniently located near grocery stores, movie theater, dining & retail shopping with quick access to Hwy 80 and I-20. See transaction desk for survey. Move-in ready.
